## Install Agent Skills

To use these skills with your AI coding assistant:

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/MicrosoftDocs/Agent-Skills.git
   ```

2. Copy skills to your assistant's skills path. See the [Agent Skills README](https://github.com/MicrosoftDocs/Agent-Skills#%EF%B8%8F-installation) for platform-specific paths.

| AI Assistant | Skills Path |
|---|---|
| **GitHub Copilot** | `.github/skills/` or `~/.copilot/skills/` |
| **Claude Code** | `.claude/skills/` or `~/.claude/skills/` |
| **OpenAI Codex** | `.codex/skills/` or `~/.codex/skills/` |
| **Cursor** | `.cursor/skills/` |
| **Gemini CLI** | `.gemini/skills/` |

